使用matplotlib画出子图¶

第一种顺序绘制,后面覆盖前面的图像¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import math


x = np.arange(1,10)
y0 = np.sqrt(x)
y1 = np.power(x,2)
y2 = np.power(x,3)
y3 = np.log2(x)

plt.subplot(2,2,1)
plt.plot(x, y0)
plt.title('sart(x)')

plt.subplot(2,2,2)
plt.plot(x, y1)
plt.title('sart(x)')

plt.subplot(2,2,3)
plt.plot(x, y2)
plt.title('sart(x)')

plt.subplot(2,2,4)
plt.plot(x, y3)
plt.title('sart(x)')

plt.show()

第二种先规划再绘制，规划网格，再填图像¶

基础版¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import math

fig = plt.figure()

sub0 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,1)
sub1 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,2)
sub2 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,3)
sub3 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,4)

x = np.arange(1,10)
y0 = np.sqrt(x)
y1 = np.power(x,2)
y2 = np.power(x,3)
y3 = np.log2(x)

sub0.plot(x, y0)
sub0.set_title("sqrt(x)")
sub1.plot(x, y1)
sub1.set_title("x^2")
sub2.plot(x, y2)
sub2.set_title("x^3")
sub3.plot(x, y3)
sub3.set_title("log2")

# plt.tight_layout()
# plt.savefig("demo.png", dpi=300)
plt.show()

sub2 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,3)
sub3 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,4)

x = np.arange(1,10)
y0 = np.sqrt(x)
y1 = np.power(x,2)
y2 = np.power(x,3)
y3 = np.log2(x)

sub0.set_title("sqrt(x)")
sub1.plot(x, y1)
sub1.set_title("x^2")

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import math

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))

sub0 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,1)
sub1 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,2)
sub2 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,3)
sub3 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,4)

x = np.arange(1,10)
y0 = np.sqrt(x)
y1 = np.power(x,2)
y2 = np.power(x,3)
y3 = np.log2(x)

sub0.plot(x, y0)
sub0.set_title("sqrt(x)")
sub1.plot(x, y1)
sub1.set_title("x^2")
sub2.plot(x, y2)
sub2.set_title("x^3")
sub3.plot(x, y3)
sub3.set_title("log2")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig("demo.png", dpi=300)
plt.show()

显示中文¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import math

plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))

sub0 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,1)
sub1 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,2)
sub2 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,3)
sub3 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,4)

x = np.arange(1,10)
y0 = np.sqrt(x)
y1 = np.power(x,2)
y2 = np.power(x,3)
y3 = np.log2(x)

sub0.plot(x, y0)
sub0.set_title("平方根sqrt(x)")
sub1.plot(x, y1)
sub1.set_title("x^2")
sub2.plot(x, y2)
sub2.set_title("x^3")
sub3.plot(x, y3)
sub3.set_title("log2")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig("demo.png", dpi=300)
plt.show()

显示多幅图像¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
from skimage import data

img1 = data.coffee()
img2 = data.camera()
img3 = data.coins()
img4 = data.cell()

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))

sub1 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,1)
sub1.set_title('coffee')
sub2 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,2)
sub2.set_title('camera')
sub3 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,3)
sub3.set_title('coins')
sub4 = fig.add_subplot(2,2,4)
sub4.set_title('cell')

sub1.imshow(img1)
sub2.imshow(img2, cmap='gray')
sub3.imshow(img3, cmap='gray')
sub4.imshow(img4, cmap='gray')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
